Mohammed Name Popularity

At NamesLook, the name Mohammed is recorded 924,193 times globally, ranking it as the 16th most common name worldwide.

Mohammed is most prevalent in Saudi Arabia, with 184,381 occurrences, making it the 7th most popular name in the country.
